                  base="i1120068"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">6.102</xref>(c). The procedures in <xref href="15.504.dita#FAR_15_504"
                  base="i1105731"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">15.504</xref>,<xref href="15.506.dita#FAR_15_506"
