                  base="i1105840"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">15.509</xref>, with reasonable modification, should be followed for sole source acquisitions and acquisitions described in <xref href="6.102.dita#FAR_6_102"
